    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help but they dont get it. they want the version of me that's easy to love, not the real one. it feels like i'm just being forced to suffer for a world that doesn't even want me here. sometimes i wonder if it would just be easier to stop trying to exist in a place that makes it so impossible to be me. it just seems like a lot of pain for nothing.",
